CHARITY AUCTION

In the name of Harambe and Koko, these beloved respective Kong representations will be minted and auctioned off on the Kadena Ecosystem. ALL of the proceeds will go straight towards the Jande Goodall Society and Food for the Hungry.

 We believe in giving back to those in need and those that inspire, and have concluded that these societies are well deserving of our donation.

This Auction was made possible, and voted on by our community of apes, Kadena Kongs!
